====================
# GENERAL SETTINGS #
=====================

# User and Group ID for container permissions
PUID="1000"
PGID="1000"

# Timezone for container environments
TIMEZONE="Europe/Berlin"

# Optional: Plex claim token (https://plex.tv/claim)
PLEX_CLAIM=""

---------------------------------------------------------------

========================
# HARDWARE TRANSCODING #
========================

# ⚠️ NVIDIA GPU transcoding is not supported in this Compose setup.
# Use Intel or AMD iGPU via /dev/dri. For NVIDIA, manual setup is required.

## Intel QuickSync iGPU or AMD GPU with VAAPI support:
HW_TRANSCODE_DEVICE="/dev/dri"

